dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Garza Peak quadrangle, Monterey, Kings and Fresno counties, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Garza Peak, CA 1953, photoinspected 1976, AMS 1955 I NW -- Series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
